title: S1: audioBoom Q&A Pt.3: Rabia Chaudry
description:
Rabia Chaudry talks about the response to Undisclosed and its unique relationship to Serial. This interview includes questions from Earl Adsley, Emily Lewis and Nina Porzucki.

Produced for AudioBoom by Jeremy Helton and Carl Scott. Music by @thesonicdrifter
